# Force LF for shell scripts and Dockerfiles.
# On Windows, CRLF line endings break:
#   - shell script shebangs (#!/bin/bash\r -> "required file not found")
#   - Dockerfile heredoc-generated scripts (e.g. frontend start.sh)
# which makes the Docker Compose stack fail to start.
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.Dockerfile text eol=lf
